  "texts": [
    "The (CNN) model achieved remarkable accuracy scores of 93.08% and 99.7% on the KIMORE and UI-PRMD datasets, respectively.",
    "Notably, this performance surpassed the previous research on the same dataset by 0.75% on the KIMORE dataset and 0.1% on the UI-PRMD dataset.",
    "Our tuned (CNN) and (CNN-LSTM) models yielded very close results for disease classification on the KIMORE dataset, achieving an accuracy rate of nearly 89.9% and 88.61%, respectively.",
    "Specifically, the (CNN) model outperformed the (CNN-LSTM) model by approximately 1.26%, demonstrating significantly faster training times.Despite the promising outcomes of our study, it is essential to address certain limitations.",
    "The proposed (CNN) model, while achieving remarkable performance, comes with the requirement of an additional preprocessing step."
